{
  "chapter": 66,
  "chapter_summary": "第六十六章讲述了徐子陵与寇仲逃离沈法兴追兵后，徐子陵在海边密林中独自修炼时，被沈法正率领的江南军高手包围。沈法正以\"攻心刃\"之名著称，带领李昌恒、屠力、谢玉菁、连凡、连楚等高手试图生擒徐子陵，以获取杨公宝库的下落。徐子陵凭借超凡的武艺和临场应变能力，以一敌六，展现惊人实力，最终重伤沈法正，击退江南军高手，继续向码头方向前进与寇仲会合。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "留下两个给我玩玩都不行吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "真正的分舵在盐街处，就是与我们偷盐的货仓相邻，那处抢船都方便点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你抓的那人倒合作。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不合作行吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "似乎人多了一点！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_fa_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "沈法正",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这或者是最好一个截着他们的机会，看情况他们是想逃往海外，以躲避李密的追杀令。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "李昌恒",
      "listener": "char_shen_fa_zheng",
      "text": "那小子究竟到了哪里去呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_fa_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "沈法正",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_jing",
      "text": "大总管和韩帮主早从他们的路线猜到他们要到这一带来。大总管对此事非常重视，否则怎会劳动到我们的谢仙子的大驾呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉菁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "照我看是他知机溜走了，我们就在这里布下陷阱，假若寇仲那小子能侥幸逃过韩帮主的天罗地网，就由我们来收拾他。只要能生擒其中一人，'杨公宝库'就是我们江南军的囊中物！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_ming_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "未名男子",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "小子果然嫩得可以，给我们一诈就诈了出来。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_yi_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "另一男子",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "也非全是骗他，另一个小子说不定早给擒下了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_ming_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "未名男子",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "小子你错过最后的机会了！若你刚才反身逸回密材内，说不定可给你溜掉。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_fa_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "沈法正",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "老夫沈法正，乃江南道大总管的亲兄，假若徐兄弟肯随我等回去，沈某保证以上宾之礼款待徐兄弟。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "李昌恒",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "在下鄱阳派李昌恒，我们对徐兄都好生爱惜，若能化干戈为玉帛，就是最好不过。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_chang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "李昌恒",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "屠力兄乃黄山派高手，乃大总管的左先锋，而在下则是右锋将。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉菁",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "奴家叫谢玉菁，可不要忘了！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_fa_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "沈法正",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "剩下的两位是祈山派连氏昆仲凡兄和楚兄，都是江湖上著名用鞭的好手，他们的流云鞭依老夫看不须多久就可登上『奇功绝艺』。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说完了吗？若没话说就动手吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_li",
      "speaker_name": "屠力",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不知好歹的家伙！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_fa_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "沈法正",
      "listener": "char_tu_li",
      "text": "暂且停手！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_fa_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "沈法正",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "老夫有一事相询。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_fa_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "沈法正",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "徐兄弟难道不想知道你另外那位兄弟的收场吗？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shen_fa_zheng",
      "text": "有劳关心，除非我见我那兄弟横倒地上，否则绝不会相信有人能奈得何他……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_fan",
      "speaker_name": "连凡",
      "listener": "char_lian_chu",
      "text": "怎样了！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_chu",
      "speaker_name": "连楚",
      "listener": "char_lian_fan",
      "text": "快助我行功！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_fa_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "沈法正",
      "listener": "char_li_chang_heng",
      "text": "昌恒退下。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_fa_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "沈法正",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "今天之事就此作罢，后会有期。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 308
    }
  ],
